  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "Creates \"Harter's Law\" to extend the civil statute of limitations, for injuries resulting from first degree child abuse, to thirty-five (35) years and cap civil damages recovery at five hundred thousand dollars ($500,000)."
